7539:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_INVERTED: active low or falling edge active.
7540:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_NONINVERTED: active high or rising edge active.
