7542:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter must be a value between 0x00 and 0x0F
7543:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @retval None
7544:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim.c ****   */
